snippet.title: Usagi Shima - Official Bunny Paradise Update Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2024
snippet.description:
Usagi Shima is a bunny adventure game developed by pank0. Players can now access the new Bunny Paradise Update for the game bringing 5 new bunnies, build a new bunny paradise with the island expansion, and utilize new content such as hats, toys, and more. The Bunny Paradise Update for Usagi Shima is available now for iOS and Google Play.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
